    If the SummarizeFilesWizard solution does not exist as a standalone Vite solution (i.e., the wizard is consumed only via LegalWorkspace), this task degenerates to "verify no standalone deploy needed" — skip the deploy step + document the finding. Empirical pre-flight suggests it DOES exist as a solution but verify before assuming.

    Escalation policy: if deploy fails, fix upstream FIRST (task 060), then re-run this task. Do not patch around build failures.
